表示のためBGRをRGBに変換する。\n","  plt.axis('off')\n","  plt.imshow(show_img) # matplot.libを用いて読み込んだ画像を表示します。\n","\n","# 画像の表示\n","# display(img1)\n","display(img2)\n"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":3,"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/","height":406},"executionInfo":{"elapsed":465,"status":"ok","timestamp":1756843673335,"user":{"displayName":"Hiroshi Omata","userId":"13724694233961387380"},"user_tz":-540},"id":"gcJAUbD8_cjB","outputId":"bb0a5b3f-8f69-44df-a2c7-6a5c77efeda3"},"outputs":[{"output_type":"display_data","data":{"text/plain":["<Figure size 640x480 with 1 Axes>"],"image/png":"\n"},"metadata":{}}],"source":["# グレースケール変換\n","# from_img = cv2.cvtColor(img1, cv2.COLOR_RGB2GRAY)\n","gray1 = cv2.cvtColor(img1,cv2.COLOR_BGR2GRAY)\n","gray2 = cv2.cvtColor(img2,cv2.COLOR_BGR2GRAY)\n","\n","#  AKAZE検出器の生成\n","akaze = cv2.AKAZE_create()\n","\n","# gray1にAKAZEを適用、特徴点を検出\n","key_point1, descriptions1 = akaze.detectAndCompute(gray1,None)\n","# gray2にAKAZEを適用、特徴点を検出\n","key_point2, descriptions2 = akaze.detectAndCompute(gray2,None)\n","\n","# キーポイントの表示\n","extraceted_img1 = cv2.drawKeypoints(gray1, key_point1, None, flags=4)\n","extraceted_img2 = cv2.drawKeypoints(gray2, key_point2, None, flags=4)\n","display(extraceted_img2)"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":4,"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/","height":348},"executionInfo":{"elapsed":673,"status":"ok","timestamp":1756843681448,"user":{"displayName":"Hiroshi Omata","userId":"13724694233961387380"},"user_tz":-540},"id":"UN2UwAnxADN5","outputId":"20beccb2-31e6-4882-ee16-675d34e4de3a"},"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["matches_length=173\n"]},{"output_type":"display_data","data":{"text/plain":["<Figure size 640x480 with 1 Axes>"],"image/png":"\n"},"metadata":{}}],"source":["def match(img1, img2):\n","    # 各画像の特徴点を取る\n","    key_point1, descriptions1 = akaze.detectAndCompute(img1,None)\n","    key_point2, descriptions2 = akaze.detectAndCompute(img2,None)\n","\n","    # BFMatcherオブジェクトの生成\n","    #  bf_matcher = cv2.BFMatcher_create(cv2.NORM_HAMMING, True)\n","    bf_matcher = cv2.BFMatcher(cv2.NORM_HAMMING, crossCheck=True)\n","    # 2つの特徴点をマッチさせる\n","    matches = bf_matcher.match(descriptions1, descriptions2)\n","\n","    # matchesをdescriptorsの似ている順にソートする\n","    matches = sorted(matches, key = lambda x:x.distance)\n","    matches_length = len(matches) # マッチした本数\n","\n","    # 特徴点同士を線でつなぐつなぐ画像を作成 (線は似ている順の先頭30本まで表示)\n","    match_img = cv2.drawMatches(img1, key_point1, img2, key_point2, matches[:30], None, flags = cv2.DrawMatchesFlags_NOT_DRAW_SINGLE_POINTS)\n","\n","    return match_img, matches_length\n","\n","# 画像のロード\n","match_img, matches_length= match(img1, img2)\n","display(match_img)\n","print(f\"matches_length={matches_length}\")\n"]}],"metadata":{"colab":{"provenance":[]},"kernelspec":{"display_name":"Python 3","name":"python3"},"language_info":{"name":"python"}},"nbformat":4,"nbformat_minor":0}
